  "title": "🚀 Recruitment Coordinator (Temp) | Immediate Start!",
  "description": "<p>Join CREW by HRnetGroup, where speed meets people connection! We’re the powerhouse behind high-volume hiring and workforce solutions, matching thousands of talents to meaningful roles across industries!</p><p>📍 <strong>Location:</strong> Orchard<br />🕗 <strong>Working Hours:</strong> 8:30am – 5:30pm<br />📅 <strong>Working Days:</strong> Monday – Friday<br />📆 <strong>Duration:</strong> Immediate – 3 months (extendable / convertible)<br />💸 <strong>Salary:</strong> $12/hour</p><p><strong>💼 What You’ll Be Doing</strong></p><ul><li>Learn to craft and post job advertisements </li><li>Shortlist and interview candidates for exciting job opportunities and campaigns</li><li>Take part in mass group hirings for exciting projects</li></ul><p><strong>💖 Why You’ll Love This Role</strong></p><ul><li>Get hands-on exposure to the recruitment and HR industry</li><li>Learn from experienced mentors in one of Asia’s leading HR companies</li><li>Sharpen your communication and coordination skills</li><li>Be part of a fun, collaborative, and fast-moving team that celebrates wins together</li></ul><p><strong>✅ Who We’re Looking For</strong></p><ul><li>Energetic, driven, and people-oriented individuals</li><li>Confident communicators who love connecting with others</li><li>Organised, proactive, and eager to learn</li><li>Completed GCE A-Level / Diploma / Degree (any field)</li></ul>",
